---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Words Containing IA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy"
  description="Complete list of Scrabble words containing IA with scores, definitions, and strategic tips. Master IA words for better Scrabble plays."
  keywords="scrabble words containing ia, ia words scrabble, words with ia, scrabble ia word list, ia scrabble strategy"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Containing IA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy",
    "description": "Complete list of Scrabble words containing IA with scores, definitions, and strategic tips.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-15",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-containing-ia" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring IA words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Top IA words include DIALYZE (20 pts), BIAXIAL (16 pts), FAMILIAR (13 pts), SPECIAL (11 pts), and TRIVIAL (10 pts). IA appears in many scientific and formal English words." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many Scrabble words contain IA?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Over 800 valid Scrabble words contain IA. Common examples include DIAL, TRIAL, SOCIAL, SPECIAL, MATERIAL, RADIAL, TRIVIAL, SPATIAL, FAMILIAR, and OFFICIAL." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What strategy works best with IA tiles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "IA often appears in word endings (-IAL, -IAN, -IAR). TRIAL (5 pts) and DIAL (5 pts) are efficient short plays. SPECIAL (11 pts) and SOCIAL (8 pts) use common tiles. IA helps dump two vowels while building longer words toward bingo bonuses." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Letter Pair Content</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Containing IA — Scrabble Word List & Strategy</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>4 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">IA is a vowel-heavy pair that appears in over 800 Scrabble words, especially in formal and scientific vocabulary. It commonly ends words via -IAL (TRIAL, SOCIAL, SPECIAL) and -IAN (MEDIAN, GUARDIAN). DIALYZE (20 pts) is the premium target. SPECIAL (11 pts) and SPATIAL (9 pts) deliver solid scores from common tiles while helping dump two vowels in one play.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top IA Words by Score</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">DIALYZE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">20</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">To separate by dialysis</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">BIAXIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Having two axes</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">FAMILIAR</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">13</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Well known</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SPECIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Distinct from others</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MATERIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Physical substance</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">TRIVIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Of little importance</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SPATIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Relating to space</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">SOCIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Relating to society</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">RADIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Arranged like rays</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">TRIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A test or legal hearing</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">DIAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A numbered face</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">800+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid IA words</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">9 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Average score</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Common</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pair rarity</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for IA Words</h2>

      <p>IA is a vowel dump pair — it uses two vowels in adjacent positions, which is invaluable when your rack is vowel-heavy. The -IAL ending (TRIAL, SOCIAL, SPECIAL, SPATIAL, TRIVIAL) is extremely productive. FAMILIAR (13 pts) reaches bingo territory as an 8-letter word. DIAL and TRIAL are reliable short plays that clear vowels efficiently.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">DIALYZE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">BIAXIAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">16 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FAMILIAR</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">13 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SPECIAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MATERIAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">10 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">TRIVIAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">10 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">IA provides <span class="text-white font-medium">800+ words and serves as a powerful vowel dump combination</span>. The -IAL suffix pattern (SOCIAL, SPECIAL, TRIVIAL) is extremely productive. DIALYZE (20 pts) is the premium play, while DIAL (5 pts) and TRIAL (5 pts) efficiently clear vowels when your rack is overloaded.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/words-containing-qu" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words Containing QU — Essential Scrabble Q Words</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/words-with-multiple-vowels" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words With Multiple Vowels — Scrabble Vowel Dumps</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/four-letter-words-every-player-should-know" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Four-Letter Words Every Scrabble Player Should Know</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every IA word from your tiles — instant results, no signup</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
